quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  7,100,"Abaffe tekitegeerekeka eri abo abasikira e nsi oluvanyuma lw’abagibaddemu okufa nti, singa twayagala twalibavunaanye olw’e byonoono bya bwe, ne tuteeka e nvumbo ku mitima gyabwe nebaba nga tebawulira"
  7,101,"E bitundu e byo tukutegeeza e bimu ku byafaayo byabyo, era mazima ababaka baabwe baabajjira n’obunnyonnyofu, baali tebayinza kukkiriza ebyo bye baalimbisa mu kusooka, bulijjo bwatyo Katonda bwazibikira e mitima gy’a bakafiiri"
  7,102,"Era abasinga obungi mu bo tetwabasanga na ndagaano yonna (gye baatuukiriza), wabula twasanga abasinga obungi mu bo nga boonoonyi"
  7,103,"Ate oluvanyuma lwabwe, twatuma Musa ewa Firawo n’abakungube, nga tumuwadde eby’amagero byaffe nebabiwakanya, kale nno, fumiitiriza olabe e nkomerero y’aboonoonyi nga bwe yali"
  7,104,"Musa naagamba nti, owange Firawo mazima nze ndi mubaka okuva ewa Mukama Katonda omulabirizi w’ebitonde"
  7,105,"Kikakafu okuba nga soogera ku Katonda okugyako amazima, mazima mbaleetedde okuva ewa Mukama omulabirizi wa mmwe obujulizi, n’olwekyo mpa abaana ba Israil (ngende nabo)"
  7,106,"(Firawo) naagamba nti oba olina obujulizi bwozze nabwo buleete, bwoba nga ddala oli mu boogera amazima"
  7,107,"Awo Musa n’asuula omuggogwe, okugenda okwekanga nga gwo, musota ogwannamaddala"
  7,108,"Era naggyayo omukonogwe, okugenda okulaba nga mweru eri buli atunula"